<p>Here is one topic that is always a hot button subject for many Sikhs. Typically most Sikhs refrain from eating meat, however there are many mixed opinions and practices. In this video Guruka Singh answers a SikhNet user&#8217;s question about this topic and hopefully gives you some new things to think about.&nbsp; </p>
