		<feedburner:origLink>http://www.mrsikhnet.com/2011/01/31/meditation-for-prosperity/</feedburner:origLink></item>
		<item>
		<title>Manifesting Prosperity and Abundance</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/MrsikhnetAudio/~3/94q9kJNaB_4/</link>
		<comments>http://www.mrsikhnet.com/2011/01/28/manifesting-prosperity-abundance/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 28 Jan 2011 23:38:52 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>gmustuk@sikhnet.com (www.MrSikhNet.com)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Featured Articles]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Guruka Singh]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Charity]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[dasvandh]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Projection]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Prosperity]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[The Secret]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Tithing]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.mrsikhnet.com/?p=35862</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[This is the first in the latest series of new SikhNet Inspiration videos with Guruka Singh.&#160; SikhNet users sent us questions, which I then&#160; used for the interviews. There were so many questions, that we did our best to talk about as many of them as we could! We used two cameras in the videos [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;">
			<a href="http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrsikhnet.com%2F2011%2F01%2F28%2Fmanifesting-prosperity-abundance%2F"><br />
				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrsikhnet.com%2F2011%2F01%2F28%2Fmanifesting-prosperity-abundance%2F&amp;source=MrSikhNet&amp;style=normal&amp;service=ow.ly&amp;b=2" height="61" width="50" /><br />
			</a>
		</div>
<p>This is the first in the latest series of new SikhNet Inspiration videos with Guruka Singh.&nbsp; SikhNet users sent us questions, which I then&nbsp; used for the interviews. There were so many questions, that we did our best to talk about as many of them as we could! We used two cameras in the videos so you&#8217;ll actually see me asking the question, rather than a mysterious voice in the background. </p>
<p>In this video I read a question from a user who wanted to know about prosperity &amp; becoming prosperous.&nbsp; Guruka Singh, as always, shares his unique perspective on what prosperity really is and how it is not really about having lots of money. &quot;<em>Prosperity is understanding, in each moment, that whatever you need, and even more is at hand at the moment you need it. That you will always have enough to live with grace; that you will always have enough to give to others and share.</em>&quot; </p>
<p>We then talk about the Sikh concept of <a href="http://www.sikhiwiki.org/index.php/Dasvandh" title="" target="_blank">Dasvandh</a> (giving back 10%). What dasvandh means and why we should practice this. </p>
<p>The last part of the video goes into the power of projection and answering a question related to documentary called &quot;<a href="http://www.mrsikhnet.com/2006/12/19/the-secret/" title="" target="_blank">The Secret</a>&quot;. Guruka Singh shares what he says is the missing 2/3rds of what they don&#8217;t tell you.</p>
<p>The video is packed with lots of great information and worth watching a few times to let it really sink in. I hope that it inspires you to make a positive change in your life! Enjoy!</p>
<p> <iframe title="YouTube video player" class="youtube-player" type="text/html" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/tDC88n7L7hc" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="345" width="560"></iframe>
</p>
<p><strong>Did you like this video? Please consider <a href="https://secure.sikhnet.com/sikhnet/donation.nsf/wizard!openform&amp;Section=MrSikhNet" title="" target="_blank">Donating to SikhNet</a> to support the production costs of making videos like these, as well as the other services that SikhNet offers freely. Thanks!</strong></p>
<p align="center"><font size="5"><a href="http://www.mrsikhnet.com/2011/01/31/meditation-for-prosperity/" title="">Read Part 2 &#8211; Meditation for Prosperity</a></font></p>
